  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed rear dormer does not respect the largely unaltered roofscape of the terrace and therefore would appear as an incongruous addition which would be harmful to the visual unity and character of the area. The proposal does not adhere to section 2.4 of the Islington Urban Design Guide (2006), and does not accord with policies CS8 and CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy (2011); and policies D4 and D11 of the Islington Unitary Development Plan (2002). Recommend refusal."
